Description: SecuBox Kernel and System Hardening
 Kernel and system hardening for SecuBox appliances.
 .
 Features:
  - Kernel sysctl hardening (ASLR, kptr_restrict, etc.)
  - Network hardening (SYN cookies, reverse path filter)
  - Module blacklist (uncommon protocols, filesystems)
  - Security benchmark tool
 .
 Based on ANSSI/CIS benchmark recommendations.
